{"tid":2492603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冰島宣佈制裁中國","createTime":"2021-04-17T08:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T10:46:28.000Z","uid":125168,"like":512,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"54392393216af49c35dc243193ca7736fd8dfdbc","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"冰島跟隨歐盟就新疆問題制裁中方 北京制裁冰島律師反制<br />\n<br />\n冰島跟隨歐盟，就新疆人權問題制裁中國個人和實體，引起中方不滿，召見冰島駐華大使抗議。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐冰島大使館發聲明，批評冰島的做法違反國際法，嚴重損害雙邊關係，決定對冰島相關人員實施同等制裁。冰島傳媒報道，被制裁的是當地一名律師，曾經在報章撰文批評中國，已經被中國列入黑名單，是冰島目前唯一被中國制裁的人。冰島外交部長對有公民被制裁感到驚訝，認為他只是行使憲法賦予的言論自由，對中方制裁表示抗議。 <br />\n<br />\n外電報道，這名律師所寫的文章，去年10月已刊登，主要批評中國使館擁有的房地產問題、中國在全球疫情大流行的角色、以及中國遊客的問題等。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2387649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2387649&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=e24d843b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2387649</a>"},{"pid":"e10a7ed39952bf195e8a716b09e6999beb8eb1d8","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C4pHKSX6wRA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC4pHKSX6wRA&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=3e83ae6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C4pHKSX6wRA</a>"},{"pid":"577439a43035f829fb6f221a5af5f65b4e3ee9dd","tid":2492603,"uid":308440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"又加速"},{"pid":"7f24395ec5d780817776186e77d398ae93f8f04d","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"577439a43035f829fb6f221a5af5f65b4e3ee9dd","tid":2492603,"uid":308440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"又加速"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"h